{"tid":1735980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推畀蘋果見到 唔好用自首嘅字眼！！！！","createTime":"2019-11-18T16:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T02:51:20.000Z","uid":72962,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b28d9aee420eb774b649a5125dd5b3f4de780a06","tid":1735980,"uid":72962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:18:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191118/60282897?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191118%2F60282897%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=rVb%2FtPUztGFmJk27tPFGPkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=1f8985e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191118%2F60282897%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=8597494b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191118/60282897?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日起包圍理工大學一日一夜，數百人被困校內，警方水炮車不斷向校方射水，部份人被催淚水劑濺中，須用凍水沖身，不少人出現低溫症。紅十字會急救志願醫療團隊下午獲准進入理大為傷者進行急救，警方呼籲校內人士自首，截至晚上9時許，有約70多人自首。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【抗暴之戰】民間漫畫界高手聚集 以筆抗爭與國際社會connect<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">由傍晚6時開始，陸續有傷者由救護人員陪同步出理大，至晚上9時許，已有約70多名傷者自首</span></span>，眾人被帶往理大附近的康達徑旅巴停車場臨時救護站，分批坐在地上，由大批警員嚴密看守下接受初步治理。現場所見，大部份人都非常虛弱及疲倦，有人更疑出現低溫症，救護員立即用錫紙將傷者包裹保溫。其後，傷者依警方指示排隊雙手搭前者膊頭，分別登上救護車或警車離開。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢哋只係一般人士尋求醫療協助！<br />\n蘋果見到嘅話<br />\n唔該改曬所有稿件<br />\n呢班人無罪<br />\n唔係自首！"},{"pid":"fecbc856f0f969d02828ee72ea3c8aabaa724b55","tid":1735980,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:19:42.000Z","msg":"毒果終於露底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f987ffcfa8cb8c434d7ca7dbe5908ad080f16c1","tid":1735980,"uid":72962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:20:00.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"785b11dbdc0b343f03f8284a1e2906ac06f3b489","tid":1735980,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:20:41.000Z","msg":"自首即係認罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdbf80b439767f77210d0f71a4fddb1bb1688efa","tid":1735980,"uid":72962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:20:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a2076f8bd5782e383e161f302eff9937a18f2db","tid":1735980,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:21:09.000Z","msg":"[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"db830c6f7d177eff83db702577302796c71f44b3","tid":1735980,"uid":164509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:21:17.000Z","msg":"屌 推 正視聽"},{"pid":"e48b91bbd9c9814569f726357b79029209e00663","tid":1735980,"uid":301361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩叫自首啊！！！！"},{"pid":"5c837f1367111358ca212e12a180b4f86beda3c4","tid":1735980,"uid":217405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:21:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7538a5ac31aad9e47cdfd197d051693bbd10418c","tid":1735980,"uid":309002,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:21:36.000Z","msg":"傷者黎架<br />\n改字眼啦"},{"pid":"48e4c659dc7ff04ea7a1dfc1c82681c288bb67